General Information

High protein post-workout shake or snack, packing over 30g of protein per serving. Whey protein contributes to the maintenance of muscle mass

Common Uses

Use as the perfect post-workout shake (within 30 minutes of your work out) or snack

Ingredients

Whey Protein Concentrate (milk), Cocoa Powder (7%), Natural Flavourings, Xanthan Gum (thickener), Sucralose (sweetener)

Directions

Add 40g (4 scoops) to 400mls of water or milk and shake well
